= *Avanti!* burns!

The Milan branch of *Avanti!* has been attacked and burned to the ground, and responsibility points to Mussolini and his Fasces of Combat. This will severely impact our ability to spread our message in Milan.

- @burning_reaction: It has been made clear what their stance is.

@burning_reaction
subtitle: Our forces are already preparing to strike the Fasci back.
